Combined 808/606 + SH-101 Groovebox for SuperCollider

How to use:
1. Open this file in SuperCollider.
2. Select all and evaluate.
3. Press PLAY.
4. Type a preset name and press SAVE. Saved presets appear in the RECALL menu.

This patch combines an 808/606 style drum machine and an SH-101 style
monosynth sequencer on one shared 16th-note clock. The synth has sends
to tape delay and reverb.
